  <div class="max-width" data-au="flex-container flex-vertical medium-gap">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>
        <span class="highlight-container">Do we make updates to this policy?</span>
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="section-content" data-au="flex-container flex-vertical medium-gap">
      <p>We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. The updated version will be indicated by an updated "Revised" date and the updated version will be effective as soon as it is accessible. We update the Cookie Policy in order to reflect any changes in cookie use, or for operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. Therefore, we ask you to revisit this Cookie Policy regularly to stay informed about our use of cookies and related technologies.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

